items.name: Image Comics Database
items.title: Image Comics Database
items.headline: Welcome to the Image Comics Wiki
items.desc:
Image is a comics and graphic novels publisher formed in 1992 by seven of Marvel Comics’ best-selling artists. Since that time, Image has gone on to become the third largest comics publisher in the United States.

The wiki is a database of all things Image related, including information on some of the more recognizable comics like Spawn and Witchblade.

items.name: Albion British Comics Database Wiki
items.title: Albion British Comics Database Wiki
items.headline: Explore the worlds of the Albion British Comics Database Wiki
items.desc: The Albion British Comics Database Wiki is dedicated to the ongoing history of British comic titles, British comic characters, British comic creators and anything else to do with...well, British comics, really! Whether you're into the earliest illustrated story papers or last week's new releases, from 2000AD to the Beano to Deadline or Viz, if it's connected to comics and originates in the UK, it belongs here. And if isn't here already-feel free to correct that!

items.name: Women In Comics Wiki
items.title: Women In Comics Wiki
items.headline: Learn more about Women in Comics!
items.desc: Comics have long been a male-dominated field, but they have never been exclusively male. Female creators have been around since the beginning, as writers, artists, editors, even owners of comic book publishers. Women are still growing in prominence in today's market, though they're still in the minority. We wanted an area independent of any other wiki or database to really focus on women's contributions to comics. In addition, we recognize that not all creators qualify as "notable" by the Other Wiki's standards, and this is a place where they can be included regardless.

items.name: Wiki DC Comics
items.title: Wiki DC Comics
items.headline: Bienvenido a la base de datos de DC Comics
items.desc:
DC Comics es una editorial estadounidense dedicada a la realización y venta de cómics fundada en 1937. Las iniciales DC son una abreviatura de Detective Comics, uno de los primeros títulos emblemáticos de la compañía. Recientemente ha sido adquirida como empresa subsidiaria de AOL-Time Warner.

Se trata de una de las mayores compañías de cómics a nivel mundial. Entre algunos sus títulos más conocidos se encuentran Superman, Batman, la Mujer Maravilla, la Liga de la Justicia, Flash y Linterna Verde. Durante décadas DC Comics ha sido una de las dos mayores compañías de cómics en Estados Unidos, siendo la otra Marvel Comics. Su sede se encuentra en Nueva York.

items.name: Ducktales New Comics Wiki
items.title: Ducktales New Comics Wiki
items.headline: Ducktales New Comics Wiki
items.desc: This wikia is dedicated to the Ducktales comics produced by Kaboom and the new Ducktales game DuckTales: Remastered! DuckTales is back! The hit Disney Afternoon TV show makes a splash this month as an all-new, original ongoing comic book series! This is the latest and greatest of the Disney Afternoon Revolution that "might solve a mystery," but will definitely "rewrite history"! Capcom announced  at their PAX East panel that they're resurrecting the beloved DuckTales platformer. Developed by Wayforward and Capcom, DuckTales: Remastered is something of a remake based on the original Nintendo version of DuckTales. It'll be out this summer for Xbox Live, PSN, and Wii U.
